{"problem": "If $\\mathbf{v} \\times \\mathbf{w} = \\begin{pmatrix} 2 \\\\ 7 \\\\ -13 \\end{pmatrix},$ then find $\\mathbf{w} \\times \\mathbf{v}.$", "solution": "We have that\n\\[\\mathbf{w} \\times \\mathbf{v} = -\\mathbf{v} \\times \\mathbf{w} = \\boxed{\\begin{pmatrix} - 2 \\\\ -7 \\\\ 13 \\end{pmatrix}}.\\]"}